{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AND INTERWIKIS AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE -->
{{tsh|wtp}}
Makes a box to link to [[Wiktionary]] just like {{tl|Wiktionary}}, but this template works just like [[Wikipedia:Piped link|piped linking]]:

===Usage===

 <nowiki>{{</nowiki>Wiktionary pipe|''actual link''|''displayed term''<nowiki>}}</nowiki>

====Examples====

{{Wiktionary pipe|tree#English|tree}}
 <nowiki>{{Wiktionary pipe|tree#English|tree}}</nowiki>

{{Wiktionary pipe|πᾶν|πᾶν (pan)|πᾶς|πᾶς (pas)}}
 <nowiki>{{Wiktionary pipe|πᾶν|πᾶν (pan)|πᾶς|πᾶς (pas)}}</nowiki>

{{Wiktionary pipe|鹿威し|shishiodoshi}}
 <nowiki>{{Wiktionary pipe|鹿威し|shishiodoshi}}</nowiki>

Leave out the "displayed term" to use the "actual link" in its place:

{{Wiktionary pipe|square bracket||Unsupported titles/Square brackets|<nowiki>[&nbsp;]</nowiki>}}
 <nowiki>{{Wiktionary pipe|square bracket||Unsupported titles/Square brackets|&lt;nowiki>[&amp;nbsp;]&lt;/nowiki>}}</nowiki>

===Location===
[[File:Sister link template columns problem.jpg|thumb|If using a large, graphical template produces odd layout problems, like the excessive white space shown on the right of this screenshot, then switch to a different sister template.]]
{{-}}
'''If placing this template in a section all by itself, put on a line all by itself, without indentation or bullets, like so:'''
*<code><nowiki>{{Wiktionary pipe|five|two and two}}</nowiki></code> →
{{Wiktionary pipe|five|two and two}}
{{-}}
{{cross}} '''Do not place this template in a section containing columns.'''

This template should normally be placed at the ''top'' of the ==External links== section at the end of an article, if the article has a section for [[WP:EL|external links]].  If no such section exists, then please place it at the top of the last section in the article. 

On [[WP:DAB|disambiguation pages]], this template should be listed above other text, but below any cleanup templates, images, infoboxes or navboxes.<!-- Per WP:ACCESS, cleanup templates, images, infoboxes, and navboxes are always first. -->  

See [[Wikipedia:Wikimedia sister projects#Where to place links]] for more information and alternatives.

===See also===
{{Wiktionary templates common doc}}

